nodes.text: HoloNet News Vol. 531 #51 was one of many in-universe HoloNet News issues published shortly before the release of Attack of the Clones. This issue was released April 11, 2002.

In the article Activists Deface Jedi Temple Lobby, Thrynka Padaunete's line "Who watches the watchmen?" is a direct reference to a real-world popular Watchmen comic limited series, where this line serves as a slogan, raising questions about costumed crime-fighters who stand above society and its rules, much like how Padaunete views the Jedi.
